output:
Map {
User Stories {
  Display Basketball Scores: As a user, I want to be able to view the current scores of basketball games.
  View Team Rosters: As a user, I want to be able to view the rosters of teams.
  View Player Stats: As a user, I want to be able to view the stats of individual players.
  Follow Teams: As a user, I want to be able to follow teams and receive notifications when they play.
  View Schedules: As a user, I want to be able to view the schedules of teams.
  View Standings: As a user, I want to be able to view the standings of teams.
  View Highlights: As a user, I want to be able to view highlights of games.
  View News: As a user, I want to be able to view news related to basketball.
  View Player Profiles: As a user, I want to be able to view the profiles of players.
}

Functionality {
  Login/Signup: As a user, I want to be able to login or signup to the application.
  Search: As a user, I want to be able to search for teams, players, and games.
  Customize Notifications: As a user, I want to be able to customize notifications for teams and players.
  Share Content: As a user, I want to be able to share content with friends.
  Save Content: As a user, I want to be able to save content for later viewing.
  Comment: As a user, I want to be able to comment on content.
  Rate Content: As a user, I want to be able to rate content.
}

Design {
  Responsive Design: As a user, I want the application to be responsive and work on all devices.
  Intuitive UI: As a user, I want the application to have an intuitive user interface.
  Accessibility: As a user, I want the application to be accessible to all users.
  Personalization: As a user, I want to be able to personalize the application to my preferences.
}

Security {
  Authentication: As a user, I want the application to have secure authentication.
  Data Protection: As a user, I want the application to protect my data.
  Encryption: As a user, I want the application to use encryption to protect my data.
}
}
